data.description: No need to look any further. This exceptional home has what you have been looking for. 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths. Open floor plan with a large great room and updated kitchen that features, quartz counter tops, marble back splash, island, hands free faucet, stainless steel appliances, and plenty of storage. The bay window looks out over the gorgeous back yard with large paver patio, pergola, and beautiful landscaping. Enjoy relaxing or entertaining in the privacy of your backyard with no houses behind you and new privacy fence. Owners suite has a full bath and walk in closet. Full basement is partially finished for extra living space and room for an office or playroom. Canal Winchester Schools with Columbus taxes. You don't want to miss this one.
